-- Reset varibales per debtor (uses to update DEBB)
Else get existing total in client currency

SQL_STMT_U.val: select cast (sum(inva_actaspecial) as decimal (14,2)), cast(sum(inva_actaextrafin) as decimal (14,2)), cast(sum(inva_actafactoring) as decimal (14,2)), cast(sum(inva_actadisputes) as decimal (14,2)) from :1/inva, :1/invo where inva_no = invo_no and invo_debc_no = :2 and invo_markcodespec = :3 and invo_aactuali <> 0 and inva_currency = ':4' for fetch only optimize for 100 rows

Text.val: // Check if the last used currency = PI.CURRENCYNEW, for every distinct
LCCH_ADMNO, LCCH_CLNTNO, LCCH_LDGR_NO, new since 19.02.2004 SCR5532 SH

SQL_STMT_U.val: select cast (sum(dcmc_specialaccounth) as decimal (14,2)), cast (sum(dcmc_extrafinanceh) as decimal (14,2)) , cast (sum(dcmc_specialaccountc) as decimal (14,2)), cast (sum(dcmc_extrafinancec) as decimal (14,2)) , cast (sum(dcmc_disputesgrossc) as decimal (14,2)) , cast (sum(dcmc_disputesgrossh) as decimal (14,2)) from :1/dcmc where dcmc_mark_code=:2 and dcmc_admno=:3 and dcmc_clntno=:4 for fetch only optimize for 100 rows
